    "_postman_id": "cv-agent-api-0001-4a7b-9c2d-refold00demo",
    "name": "CloudVision CRM \u2014 Agent & App APIs",
    "description": "Validation collection for the CloudVision CRM demo.\n\nTwo auth models:\n\u2022 **Agent API (token)** \u2014 Bearer {{agent_token}}, what Refold calls.\n\u2022 **Session API (cookie)** \u2014 run 'login' first; Postman reuses the session cookie automatically.\n\nTip: use the Collection Runner to execute everything in order. The Agent folder self-populates {{meeting_id}}/{{account_id}}/{{user_id}} from the live meetings list.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{agent_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
